HEADWORD: Denunciator
<hw>De*nun"ci*a`tor</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>denuntiator</ets>, <ets>-ciator</ets>, a police officer.]</ety>
<def>One who denounces, publishes, or proclaims, especially intended or
coming evil; one who threatens or accuses.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Denunciatory</ent>⟦br⟧
